
'''= open source  heavy load bicycle trailer system'''

URL = http://carlacargo.de/

=Description=

"Carla Cargo is a new concept for a heavy load bicycle trailer system. It is very stable, includes an overrun brake and engine support. It allows to transport anything you want easily, safely and comfortable. It can carry up to 1.2m² and around 250kg of goods. We want to act as social business startup and try actually our best to prepair everything for start of production."

